{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"68217227eb","title":"歪曲整风运动的言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"87fc3aee32","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"68217227eb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1a4ad5356d","name":"广州市工商界"},{"id":"9058322a90","name":"郑赞"},{"id":"9811aa61da","name":"汤博文"},{"id":"d0349fbd39","name":"凌志荣"},{"id":"de11ce0f72","name":"刘文亮"},{"id":"ee4076c588","name":"蔡凯元"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a167129bf7","type":"title","text":"歪曲整风运动的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"49bfcfb41f","type":"authors","text":"广州市工商界汤博文刘文亮郑赞凌志荣蔡凯元","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"4fcf8798f3","type":"paragraph","text":"汤博文：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"6698fa27e0","type":"paragraph","text":"虽然目前有国务院的直接支持，谁也不敢报复，但是事后我看问题会来的，打击报复是避免不了的，过去各个运动事例说明这一点。（注：意思是鸣放后会受打击）。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"ddcb8e46fc","type":"paragraph","text":"刘文亮：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"0cbeee353c","type":"paragraph","text":"现在政府大力宣传和鼓励“争鸣”，但是大多数人还是不敢鸣，因为搞过反胡风，大家都怕，将来一个运动就吃不消。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"76d48eabbf","type":"paragraph","text":"郑赞：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"7955b31528","type":"paragraph","text":"讲到埋身一般是有顾虑，是否每个党员对鸣放都认识清楚，这是一个问题，如有一个学院出墙报，党支书要看原稿和笔者姓名，使鸣放有顾虑。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"7fcc0fa756","type":"paragraph","text":"凌志荣：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"043a8bf8f8","type":"paragraph","text":"整风运动是形式主义，是真主意假商量，现在矛盾咁多，不知如何争、如何鸣，都是没有作用，因为天下是共产党打来的，如果有些改变的话，都是形式主义，真主意，假商量的。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"5d3c1821b9","type":"paragraph","text":"蔡凯元：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"8fce6fa6b9","type":"paragraph","text":"讲话讲得多了，难免就有错，爱之者、言之切，葛佩琦的言论有好处也有坏处，他不放出来，党就不知，放出来了，纔能深入了解群情，如果一下子扣大帽子那是不好的，要做到“言者无罪，闻者足戒”。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"},{"id":"bcb8e10de7","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《广州市工商界错误的右派的言论汇编》（第一辑），中共广州市委社会反右办公室编印，1958年4月10日。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb"}],"page":{"id":"37e1394ece","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68217227eb","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}